{"tid":140450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來奪麵雙琪事件係甘比揭發","createTime":"2017-03-02T07:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T15:37:14.000Z","uid":53000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"543e4e3ccf74ebe9b25c5b7d61f3857c5fae6e95","tid":140450,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"98年入行做娛記，1萬蚊月薪<br />\n一年後影到好勝gg喺浩南哥屋企慶<br />\n喺娛記中上位<br />\n一年後追訪小小超同林慧儀緋聞，<br />\n衝上去揭開林慧儀前額頭髮影佢正面樣<br />\n<br />\n一年後少林足球慶功宴俾周星馳meet面珠登<br />\n同年大劉同王穎妤緋聞，甘比衝前影大劉，<br />\n大劉發老皮鬧佢做乜咁近影佢<br />\n甘比還擊: 你驚我影到你粒大黑墨呀<br />\n<br />\n08年甘比生左個女<br />\n呂麗君出公開信話未知女嬰父親係邊個既情況下，<br />\n我同我老公會在能力範圍內提供協助<br />\n<br />\n點知激嬲大劉，大劉話唔高興隨時可以走"},{"pid":"f55b3de4134601894ade1e716b95214ca1a141f0","tid":140450,"uid":21871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n甘比還擊: 你驚我影到你粒大黑墨呀<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n咁就做到十大富豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314641cc2a3281ed2041b2e69dafe4f64b642dd0","tid":140450,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:59:35.000Z","msg":"佢同大劉真係幾似電視劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18934496a261bbaa1c7382abd8f1cfd75a952b41","tid":140450,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"反而呂麗君係英國倫敦大學化學博士"},{"pid":"e7c45627b0789a7557b859d8a6310af0976a46ce","tid":140450,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:02:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fbe99320b7453e9e2b4cdf7a944da0e853f7b9c","tid":140450,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"641306eb784e427fa3c66a5f948603d2350f76a1","tid":140450,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"甘比個名係來自娛樂金魚眼條粉紅色金魚"},{"pid":"7f721363d915675102b4bb805fababac3b94c629","